entries.title_d: You are ordered to fly to the designated areas and inspect suspicious Rebel craft to try and catch Imperial terrorist infiltrators.
entries.title: Dathomir system: Investigate suspicious Rebel craft.
entries.split_quest_alert: Rebel Command: < We are showing multiple TIE Interceptor ships incoming, the spy must have had a hidden guard. Prepare for battle! >
entries.quest_location_d: The Dathomir system is always dangerous, even when you're in a area controlled by us like this one so stay sharp.
entries.quest_inspect_d: If you find a ship with a bomb or other similar device, disable it at once and dock with it to secure the threat.
entries.quest_dock_d: Dock with the disabled traitor ship and disarm that thermal bomb.
